                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <p>Columns: 3;
                                                  ruled lines: 41;
                                                  written lines: 40; Uniform layout. Leviticus, Esther, Song of Songs and Hafṭarot commence a new leaf. Initial words of each book written in larger letters. Masoretic calculations at the end of Genesis and Leviticus. No Masorah magna or parva, although the ruling for both of them is provided. Visible pricking and ruling with sharp object on the hair-side of folios. </p>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
